Project Introduction

This project presents a simple interactive website about the vocal any group . 
The goal of the project is to demonstrate the use of basic web technologies such as HTML, 
CSS, and JavaScript in creating a functional and visually organized webpage.

The website includes a header with the group name and logo, a navigation menu,
buttons for each singer, modal windows with images and descriptions, and a contact
form for performance requests. Modal windows allow the user to view additional information
without leaving the main page, which improves user interaction and page organization.

The purpose of this project is to practice structuring a webpage, designing elements with
CSS, and adding interactivity using JavaScript. Through this project, the basic principles
of modern web development and user interface design are demonstrated.